Pre - Installation:
===================
- Only for i686 Copatible machines.
- Min 256MB Ram and 800MB Disk Space.
- Download the Arch Image from "https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Category:Getting_and_installing_Arch" 
- You will be logged in as Root and given Zsh Shell prompt.
- Internet Connections is required, since the installation packages are in the remote server.
- 
